{"tid":1536193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想 贏 嘅 巴 絲 入 嚟 推 post | 有 關 九 月 八 日 活 動 事 宜","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:20:27.000Z","uid":71085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a50fc1961d85d4326c5bf1794be2500cfb781791","tid":1536193,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDonald Trump 神之一手已打出　不過無港人關注　無香港人理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535480</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n巴打呢個post推到百幾頁，我諗九成九人都無人睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多巴絲問我地可以點做，而有巴打提出整banner<br />\n所以我諗到，如果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地整一大堆banner喺九月八號舉，係咪都係另一種文宣方法？</span></span><br />\n想必然當日會有好多外媒，咁我地舉banner+嗌口號係咪可以<span style=\"color: red;\">助攻比侵又可以引起國際關注</span>？<br />\n喺呢件事上我地基本百利而無一害<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">支共認=還錢<br />\n支共唔認=Free HK</span><br />\n時日無多，大家認同嘅話推post，出到力嘅可以留言一齊整<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港  時代革命<br />\n五大訴求  缺一不可</span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91c3dd2f3cd1f08b501386442faec16c7602c2a","tid":1536193,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"906c8a84957951d51137e8dc6212c6f27df35904","tid":1536193,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr